        walkthrough = 'This Mission is triggered automatically after receiving the cutscene for Pillar of Hope.\n1. After waiting an in game day and zoning, check the Veridical Conflux in Grauberg (S) for a cutscene.\n   - The C.A (Campaign Arbiter) Warp will bring you closest to reach Witchfire Glen for this objective if you have little to no progress with Voidwatch.\n   - While waiting for the game day to change you can go farm the   that is needed for the next Mission.',
