        previous = {'Edge of Existence'},
        next = {'Forget Me Not'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = 'Obtain 4 [Key Item] Large memory fragments from the following 6 sub-quests:\n1. Her Memories: Homecoming Queen, will give you the first [Key Item] Large memory fragment.\n   - Her Memories: Old Bean\n   - Her Memories: The Faux Pas\n   - Her Memories: Grave Resolve\n     - Completing these 3 quests will combine the [Key Item] Tiny memory fragments into the first [Key Item] Large memory fragment.\n2. Her Memories: Of Malign Maladies, will give you the second [Key Item] Large memory fragment.\n     - You may want to begin this quest first, as you will be asked to wait an in-game day to complete it.\n3. Her Memories: Operation Cupid, will give you the third [Key Item] Large memory fragment.\nObtain the fourth and last [Key Item] Large memory fragment from the Nation you are allied to in the past:\n4.  San d\'Oria: Her Memories: Carnelian Footfalls\n5.  Bastok: Her Memories: Azure Footfalls\n6.  Windurst: Her Memories: Verdure Footfalls\nOnce you have 4 [Key Item] Large memory fragments, you will receive a message to return to Cait Sith, this mission is now completed and you will be on Forget Me Not.',
