        notes = '1. Galarhigg is fairly easy to defeat with a PLD/NIN and RDM/WHM.  The only difficulty occurred from Petro Eyes, which left the Paladin petrified for several minutes.\n2. "Soloed" easily with Trusts as 75 RDM/BLM.',
